            <div class="insight-title">⚖️ Prescriptive Merchandising Range Shifts</div>
            <div class="insight-text">Models passing the <b>45% active lifecycle gate</b> (Min ${densityGateLimit} selling weeks) validated for visibility adjustment:</div>
